description: Go`s Tentacool was initially not the Pokémon he was trying to catch. He had spotted another Tentacool in front of it and during the Poké Ball throw, it moved out of the way, causing the ball to hit and capture this Tentacool. Despite not being the Tentacool he was attempting to catch, Go was still please to catch a Pokémon.
name: Menokurage (Gou)
